Interface IPosition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistenceable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocationBuilder, SpongeLocationBuilder

    public interface IPosition
extends Persistenceable
    Position entity to manage calculations between positions and velocities.
